name: Hanumankind
bio: Hanumankind is an emerging hip-hop artist from India, known for his energetic rap, international collaborations, and unique sound that blends Indian identity with global hip-hop culture.

name: Samay Raina
bio: Samay Raina is a stand-up comedian and popular chess streamer, known for reviving chess in India through his streams and collaborations with grandmasters.

name: Raghav Juyal
bio: Raghav Juyal, also known as the 'King of Slow Motion', is a dancer, choreographer, and actor famous for his unique dance style and appearances in films and reality shows.
